    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s basically in showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I've babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's been loved and cared for, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
