    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. This specimen features crisp individual throttle bodies and a flawless 8,400 RPM redline. The mechanical profile is bolstered by documented rod bearing prophylaxis and throttle actuator service. The chassis dynamics remain factory-tight, benefiting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a precision-locking M-Variable differential. Zero subframe fatigue or thermal cycling issues. The exterior maintains its original luster with no orange peel or panel misalignment, reflecting its pampered, climate-controlled history. A mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
