      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a high-grade ceramic coating; there are no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule\u2014the leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the carpets are protected by original factory mats, and every electronic component operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is turn-key and performs exactly as it did the day it left the dealership, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records and a clean bill of health from a recent specialist inspection. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. Complete with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and documentation.",
